const messages = {
	signUpSuccess: "Successfully registered! You've been signed in as well.",
	signUpFailure:
	  "Registration failed. Email may be taken, or passwords don't match.",
	signInSuccess: 'Welcome!',
	signInFailure:
	  'Failed to sign in. Check your email and password and try again.',
	signOutSuccess: 'Come back soon!',
	changePasswordSuccess: 'Password changed successfully!',
	changePasswordFailure:
	  'Failed to change passwords. Check your old password and try again.',
	indexExpensesSuccess: 'Expenses retrieved successfully!',
	indexExpensesFailure: 'Failed to get expenses. Please try again.',
	showExpenseSuccess: 'Expense retrieved successfully!',
	showExpenseFailure: 'Failed to get expense. Please try again.',
	createExpenseSuccess: 'Expense created successfully!',
	createExpenseFailure: 'Something went wrong. Please try again.',
	indexDepositsSuccess: 'Deposits retrieved successfully!',
	indexDepositsFailure: 'Failed to get deposits. Please try again.',
	showDepositSuccess: 'Deposit retrieved successfully!',
	showDepositFailure: 'Failed to get deposit. Please try again.',
	createDepositSuccess: 'Deposit created successfully!',
	createDepositFailure: 'Something went wrong. Please try again.',
  };
  
  module.exports = messages;
